 completely random, you might end up with a Fetish of the Nimble (2ac 5agi 5dex 2% dodge) which isnt all that great. Most of the other drops are also not all that spiffy either but worth looting to sell. <p>Brother Lizzik : 60 Monk : Grandmaster with Turbo Fists!
